INSTALL NOTES:

FFMpeg is required for video processing, as are lots of codecs to support
the various transcodings.  I did this with MacPorts via the command:

sudo port install ffmpeg +gpl +lame +x264 +xvid +faad


REQUIRED GEMS:
- ruby-mp3info
- rubyzip


